🌐 Task 1 — Language Translation Tool
📌 What is this?


A desktop application that translates text from one language to another.


The user can:


Enter text Select source language Select target language Translate instantly


It works similarly to a mini version of Google Translate built completely in Python.


⚙️ How It Works User enters text Application reads source and target language Text is sent to Google's translation engine using the deep-translator library Translated response is returned Result is displayed instantly


Note: No paid **API** key is required.


✨ Features
🌍 Supports 20+ languages
🔍 Auto-detect source language
⇄ Swap language button
📋 Copy translated text
🗑 Clear text instantly
📊 Status bar updates
🌙 Dark-themed modern UI
🛠 Technologies Used
Technology  Purpose
Python  Core programming language
Tkinter Desktop **GUI** framework
deep-translator Google Translate integration
